  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 200 degrees Celsius.",
    "Heat olive oil in a wide skillet over medium-high heat until shimmering.",
    "Add diced onion and sauté until translucent.",
    "Stir in minced garlic, grated ginger, cumin, coriander, and turmeric, cooking for 30 seconds until fragrant.",
    "Add sliced carrot and diced tomato, cooking for 2 minutes.",
    "Add broccoli florets, season with salt and pepper, and pour in water or broth, then cover and simmer for 5 minutes.",
    "Transfer the skillet or a shallow oven-safe dish to the preheated oven and bake uncovered for 15 minutes to crisp the broccoli edges.",
    "Remove from oven, squeeze lemon juice, sprinkle chopped cilantro, and serve immediately."
